固體熱力學                              


  	1. How thermodynamics to beboring？ 2.What are th major principles of thermodynamics？ 3. why is it that a materials Science-major student need to Learn the principles of Thermodynamics？ 4. Any relationship between Thermodynamics and the Formation of the universe and lives？ 5. Has the only law of Thermodynamics, the entropy law, failed to explain any ever-existing phenomenon of the nature？ 6. A unique approach-the concept of reversible process. 7. selected topics on the application of thermodynamics in materials science, especially in solid state systems.

